\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\ql\rtlch\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe2052\hich\fs24\lang2057\loch\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 This plugin locate digital photos according to shooting time thanks to the comparison with a layer of reference points (usually the points of a GPS track). Image files must have EXIF data with the shooting time ('DateTimeOriginal' tag) and the reference la
